# Optional. The app runs fully without this — the OpenAI explainer is additive
# and degrades gracefully (missing key / failure / 8s timeout -> structured
# report renders unchanged, narration silently omitted).
#
# For local use: copy to .streamlit/secrets.toml and fill in.
# For Streamlit Cloud: paste into the app's Secrets settings, do NOT commit
# the real key.
